Package: wasted
Title: wasted: for Plastic Waste Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tyler", "Stoen", , "tyler.stoen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    person("Faran", "Igani", , "figani@calpoly.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides summaries and graphics related to plastic waste records from cleanups across the world. The package uses data provided by Sarah Suave via a blogpost titled *Break Free from Plastic*, published in a tidyteusday entry in 2021. 
